item.title: Faster EFT
item.description:
Faster EFT

How to tap yourself into a healthier and powerful mindset.

The art of tapping has it's origins in Chinese medecine. It is linked to the energetic body by specific acupressure points to lesser or abolish emotional imprints on oneself. One starts by connecting with the undesired feeling, thought or mindset and defining where it is and how it manifests in the body.Â
